Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: A high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in the society.

Name of movie: You Are So Not Invited to My Bat Mitzvah

Stars: Idina Menzel, Jackie Sandler, Adam Sandler, Sadie Sandler

Description: An abandoned dog teams up with other strays to get revenge on his former owner.

Description: An intelligence operative for a shadowy global peacekeeping agency races to stop a hacker from stealing its most valuable and dangerous weapon.

Description: Helen signs up for a wilderness survival course, a year after getting divorced. She discovers through this experience that sometimes, you have to get really lost in order to find yourself.

Description: A small-town man who falls in love with the most beautiful girl in town. He wants to marry her one day because marrying her can raise his social position.
Stars: Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Manoj Pahwa, Anjuman Saxena

Description: An eight-year-old boy tries to investigate the mysterious knocking sounds that are coming from inside the walls of his house, unveiling a dark secret that his sinister parents have kept hidden from him.

Description: Based on the unbelievable, inspiring true story of a team of underdogs - a struggling, working-class gamer, a failed former race car driver, and an idealistic motorsport exec - who risk it all to take on the most elite sport in the world.

Description: A single mom named Gabbie hires a tour guide, a psychic, a priest and a historian to help exorcise her newly bought mansion after discovering it is inhabited by ghosts.
Stars: LaKeith Stanfield, Rosario Dawson, Owen Wilson, Tiffany Haddish

Description: After an entity of mysterious origin annihilates the world's population causing those who observe it to take their lives, Sebastián and his daughter begin their own great adventure of survival in Barcelona.
Stars: Mario Casas, Georgina Campbell, Diego Calva, Naila Schuberth

Description: The story of American scientist, J. Robert Oppenheimer, and his role in the development of the atomic bomb.

Stars: Harsh Beniwal, Mohit Chhikara, Aditya Paul, Vishal Vashishtha

Description: Barbie suffers a crisis that leads her to question her world and her existence.
Stars: Margot Robbie, Ryan Gosling, Issa Rae, Kate McKinnon

Description: A straight-laced bank manager about to marry the love of his life. When his bank is held up by infamous Ghost Bandits during his wedding week, he believes his future in-laws who just arrived in town, are the infamous Out-Laws.
Stars: Adam Devine, Pierce Brosnan, Ellen Barkin, Nina Dobrev

Description: Two ex-special forces soldiers must escort a group of civilians along Baghdad's "Highway of Death" to the safety of the Green Zone.
Stars: Jackie Chan, John Cena, Chunrui Ma, Wenli Jiang

Description: The incredible true story of a former government agent turned vigilante who embarks on a dangerous mission to rescue hundreds of children from traffickers.
Stars: Jim Caviezel, Mira Sorvino, Bill Camp, Cristal Aparicio

Description: A middle-class boy in Ahmedabad, Satyaprem falling in one-sided love with Katha, who is coping with her breakup with Tapan. Through the journey, they discover each other's life and complement in accomplishing what was left halfway.
Stars: Kartik Aaryan, Kiara Advani, Supriya Pathak, Gajraj Rao

Stars: Gippy Grewal, Sonam Bajwa, Binnu Dhillon, Rupinder Rupi

Description: A tragic love story that left an indelible mark on Sumon's life, shattering his world and leaving him forever transformed.

Description: Ethan Hunt and his IMF team must track down a dangerous weapon before it falls into the wrong hands.

Description: On the brink of losing her home, Maddie finds an intriguing job listing: helicopter parents looking for someone to bring their introverted 19-year-old son out of his shell before college. She has one summer to make him a man or die trying.
Stars: Jennifer Lawrence, Andrew Barth Feldman, Laura Benanti, Matthew Broderick

Description: Barry Allen uses his super speed to change the past, but his attempt to save his family creates a world without super heroes, forcing him to race for his life in order to save the future.

Description: A young pregnant woman named Mia escapes from a country at war by hiding in a maritime container aboard a cargo ship. After a violent storm, Mia gives birth to the child while lost at sea, where she must fight to survive.
Stars: Anna Castillo, Tamar Novas, Tony Corvillo, Mariam Torres

Description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.

Description: A sick and desperate John travels to Mexico for a risky and experimental medical procedure in hopes of a miracle cure for his cancer only to discover the entire operation is a scam to defraud the most vulnerable.

Description: The friends facing disastrously funny situations together and having each other's backs through the trenches to make it out of a new mess this time.

Description: Hadley and Oliver begin to fall for each other on their flight from New York to London. The probability of ever finding each other again seems impossible, but love - and London - may have a way of defying the odds.

Description: In post-World War II Venice, Poirot, now retired and living in his own exile, reluctantly attends a seance. But when one of the guests is murdered, it is up to the former detective to once again to uncover the killer.

Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: On the brink of losing her home, Maddie finds an intriguing job listing: helicopter parents looking for someone to bring their introverted 19-year-old son out of his shell before college. She has one summer to make him a man or die trying.
Stars: Jennifer Lawrence, Andrew Barth Feldman, Laura Benanti, Matthew Broderick

Description: Barry Allen uses his super speed to change the past, but his attempt to save his family creates a world without super heroes, forcing him to race for his life in order to save the future.
Stars: Ezra Miller, Michael Keaton, Sasha Calle, Michael Shannon

Description: A young pregnant woman named Mia escapes from a country at war by hiding in a maritime container aboard a cargo ship. After a violent storm, Mia gives birth to the child while lost at sea, where she must fight to survive.
Stars: Anna Castillo, Tamar Novas, Tony Corvillo, Mariam Torres

Description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.
Stars: Kiernan Shipka, Olivia Holt, Charlie Gillespie, Lochlyn Munro

Description: A sick and desperate John travels to Mexico for a risky and experimental medical procedure in hopes of a miracle cure for his cancer only to discover the entire operation is a scam to defraud the most vulnerable.

Description: The friends facing disastrously funny situations together and having each other's backs through the trenches to make it out of a new mess this time.

Description: An exiled anxiety-ridden homebody must battle an alien who's found its way into her home.
Stars: Kaitlyn Dever, Elizabeth Kaluev, Zack Duhame, Lauren L. Murray

Description: Against the backdrop of a war between humans and robots with artificial intelligence, a former soldier finds the secret weapon, a robot in the form of a young child.
Stars: John David Washington, Madeleine Yuna Voyles, Gemma Chan, Allison Janney

Description: Hadley and Oliver begin to fall for each other on their flight from New York to London. The probability of ever finding each other again seems impossible, but love - and London - may have a way of defying the odds.
Stars: Haley Lu Richardson, Ben Hardy, Rob Delaney, Katrina Nare

Description: In post-World War II Venice, Poirot, now retired and living in his own exile, reluctantly attends a seance. But when one of the guests is murdered, it is up to the former detective to once again to uncover the killer.
Stars: Kenneth Branagh, Michelle Yeoh, Jamie Dornan, Tina Fey

Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: Tom Nichols is a hardened New England detective, unflinching in his pursuit of a case where nothing is as it seems and it begins to dismantle the illusions in his own life.

Description: A high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in the society.
Stars: Shah Rukh Khan, Nayanthara, Vijay Sethupathi, Deepika Padukone

Description: An abandoned dog teams up with other strays to get revenge on his former owner.

Description: A middle-class boy in Ahmedabad, Satyaprem falling in one-sided love with Katha, who is coping with her breakup with Tapan. Through the journey, they discover each other's life and complement in accomplishing what was left halfway.

Description: Barry Allen uses his super speed to change the past, but his attempt to save his family creates a world without super heroes, forcing him to race for his life in order to save the future.

Description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.

Description: A sick and desperate John travels to Mexico for a risky and experimental medical procedure in hopes of a miracle cure for his cancer only to discover the entire operation is a scam to defraud the most vulnerable.

Description: Hadley and Oliver begin to fall for each other on their flight from New York to London. The probability of ever finding each other again seems impossible, but love - and London - may have a way of defying the odds.

Description: In post-World War II Venice, Poirot, now retired and living in his own exile, reluctantly attends a seance. But when one of the guests is murdered, it is up to the former detective to once again to uncover the killer.

Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: A young pregnant woman named Mia escapes from a country at war by hiding in a maritime container aboard a cargo ship. After a violent storm, Mia gives birth to the child while lost at sea, where she must fight to survive.

Description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.

Description: The friends facing disastrously funny situations together and having each other's backs through the trenches to make it out of a new mess this time.

Stars: John David Washington, Madeleine Yuna Voyles, Gemma Chan, Allison Janney

Description: Hadley and Oliver begin to fall for each other on their flight from New York to London. The probability of ever finding each other again seems impossible, but love - and London - may have a way of defying the odds.

Description: In post-World War II Venice, Poirot, now retired and living in his own exile, reluctantly attends a seance. But when one of the guests is murdered, it is up to the former detective to once again to uncover the killer.

Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: A high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in the society.

Description: An abandoned dog teams up with other strays to get revenge on his former owner.

Description: A young pregnant woman named Mia escapes from a country at war by hiding in a maritime container aboard a cargo ship. After a violent storm, Mia gives birth to the child while lost at sea, where she must fight to survive.

Description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.

Description: The friends facing disastrously funny situations together and having each other's backs through the trenches to make it out of a new mess this time.

Stars: John David Washington, Madeleine Yuna Voyles, Gemma Chan, Allison Janney

Description: Hadley and Oliver begin to fall for each other on their flight from New York to London. The probability of ever finding each other again seems impossible, but love - and London - may have a way of defying the odds.

Description: In post-World War II Venice, Poirot, now retired and living in his own exile, reluctantly attends a seance. But when one of the guests is murdered, it is up to the former detective to once again to uncover the killer.

Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: A high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in the society.

Description: An abandoned dog teams up with other strays to get revenge on his former owner.

Description: A young pregnant woman named Mia escapes from a country at war by hiding in a maritime container aboard a cargo ship. After a violent storm, Mia gives birth to the child while lost at sea, where she must fight to survive.

Description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.

Description: The friends facing disastrously funny situations together and having each other's backs through the trenches to make it out of a new mess this time.

Stars: John David Washington, Madeleine Yuna Voyles, Gemma Chan, Allison Janney

Description: Hadley and Oliver begin to fall for each other on their flight from New York to London. The probability of ever finding each other again seems impossible, but love - and London - may have a way of defying the odds.

Description: In post-World War II Venice, Poirot, now retired and living in his own exile, reluctantly attends a seance. But when one of the guests is murdered, it is up to the former detective to once again to uncover the killer.

Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: A high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in the society.

Description: An abandoned dog teams up with other strays to get revenge on his former owner.

Description: A young pregnant woman named Mia escapes from a country at war by hiding in a maritime container aboard a cargo ship. After a violent storm, Mia gives birth to the child while lost at sea, where she must fight to survive.

Description: When the infamous "Sweet Sixteen Killer" returns 35 years after his first murder spree to claim another victim, 17-year-old Jamie accidentally travels back in time to 1987, determined to stop the killer before he can start.

Description: The friends facing disastrously funny situations together and having each other's backs through the trenches to make it out of a new mess this time.

Stars: John David Washington, Madeleine Yuna Voyles, Gemma Chan, Allison Janney

Description: Hadley and Oliver begin to fall for each other on their flight from New York to London. The probability of ever finding each other again seems impossible, but love - and London - may have a way of defying the odds.

Description: In post-World War II Venice, Poirot, now retired and living in his own exile, reluctantly attends a seance. But when one of the guests is murdered, it is up to the former detective to once again to uncover the killer.

Description: Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on, the Expendables are the world's last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table.

Description: A high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in the society.

Description: An abandoned dog teams up with other strays to get revenge on his former owner.
